creator: Mighty Networks
descriptionHtml:
MiMentor’s mission is to develop and support innovative mentorship opportunities that inspire the next generation of healthcare leaders for underserved communities.

Join this powerful mentoring community, share your story, learn about career development opportunities and events that connect our mentees and mentors.

Use the MiMentor app to:

+ Chat, message and collaborate securely with healthcare students and professionals
+ Gain access to healthcare mentoring opportunities, summer enrichment programs and other career development opportunities
+ Learn about upcoming events near you
+ Navigate your path when you encounter challenges that don’t have easy or obvious answers

Members of MiMentor are connecting, getting support and finding inspiration on topics like:

+ Diversity & Inclusion
+ Self Care & Wellness
+ Applying to Health Professions School
+ Mentorship Opportunities
+ #Health4All

Learn more at MiMentor.org

+ Diversity & Inclusion

+ Applying to Health Professions School
+ Mentorship Opportunities
+ #Health4All
